snippet: A passenger plane skidded past the landing strip and overturned in the eastern Ukrainian city of Donetsk on Wednesday, killing five people, officials said.
abstract: Passenger plane carrying soccer fans headed for match skids past landing strip and overturns in eastern Ukrainian city of Donetsk.
lead_paragraph: A passenger plane skidded past the landing strip and overturned in the eastern Ukrainian city of Donetsk on Wednesday, killing five people, officials said.
